We are thinking about putting a ultrasonic distance finder on our robot this year.
Does anyone have any recommendations for which one to get?
Any feedback would be greatly appreciated.
Thank you.

Ultrasonic sensors have a significant amount of drawbacks for an FRC application, their polling rate and max distance are the two main caveats as opposed to an April tag vision system. Of course it is more simple, but with the amount of background interference from all the other electronics, I wouldn’t trust it as a reliable input system.
